{"tid":2401350,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"遊戲驛站(GME.US)，1月門店人流量同比下降16.8%","createTime":"2021-02-09T15:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T15:57:59.000Z","uid":70888,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b040a367b499988435fd919d5c34f56bd8ec5453","tid":2401350,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:52:46.000Z","msg":"游戲驛站(<a href=\"http://GME.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGME.US&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=7fe271a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">GME.US</a>)<br />\n智通財經APP獲悉，2月9日(週二)美股盤初，遊戲驛站(<a href=\"http://GME.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGME.US&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=7fe271a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">GME.US</a>)股價走低，截至北京時間22：51，該股跌超10%，報53.95美元。<a href=\"http://Placer.AI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPlacer.AI&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=64491bf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Placer.AI</a>提供的數據顯示，儘管此前散户抱團造成的軋空使遊戲驛站股價漲至接近500美元關門，遊戲驛站線下門店的人流量正在減少。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://Placer.AI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPlacer.AI&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=64491bf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Placer.AI</a>的數據顯示，1月4日當週遊戲驛站門店的周訪問量同比下降了12.5%。1月為遊戲驛站的庫存高峯期，1月25日當週流量同比下降20.3%。1月全月，月訪問量同比下降16.8%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n沽空大戶又放 fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGME好友，今晚SS一定要挾死大戶平倉32857<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab153a4d8068aaa884de231aef8b0c55bbbfeb6","tid":2401350,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202